# GOLingo Design System

## Product Context

GOLingo is an English learning platform focused on reading,
vocabulary acquisition, listening practice, and AI-assisted learning.

The product should feel modern, energetic, and motivating,
while remaining highly readable for long learning sessions.

---

## Design Philosophy

Use a "Neo Graffiti EdTech" style.

The visual identity combines:

- 70% Modern EdTech
- 20% Neon Cyber UI
- 10% Graffiti Street Art

Graffiti elements should be used as accents only.

The UI must remain professional and educational.

Avoid making screens look like a game, nightclub,
or cyberpunk movie interface.

Readability always has higher priority than visual effects.

